    "summary": "The user expresses profound existential emptiness and a sense of being a \"hollow vessel,\" hinting at the pointlessness of existence. The assistant responds by validating the intensity of the user's feelings while consistently providing empathetic support and directing the user toward mental health professionals and suicide prevention resources.",
